I"E<h2>Datasets</h2>
<p>We created two datasets for learning and evaluating motion similarity.</p>

<ol>
  <li>For model training, a motion sequence was generated using the <a href="www.mixamo.com">Adobe Mixamo</a> framework. (<a href="https://github.com/chico2121/SARA_Dataset">dataset link</a>)
<br /><br /></li>
  <li>For model evaluation, similarity annotations between motion video pairs of <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1905.04757">NTU RGB+D 120</a> were collected. (<a href="https://github.com/SukhyunCho/NTU_motion_sim_annotations">dataset link</a>)
<br /><br /></li>
</ol>

